					<![CDATA[
						 <p>This was a blast to write and would not have been so fun were it not for my friend and coauthor <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/malycegraves" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4916887&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1592738779" alt="MalyceGraves" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4916887)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/malycegraves" >MalyceGraves</a></span>. They continue to impress me daily and help me figure out new ways to pump out the crazy shit we like writing. We hope you enjoy our oranges.</p> <p>P.s. How great is it that there's a Florida Department of Citrus? Cause to me that's just plain fantastic.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
